    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six factors not assessed were appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 requirements for MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications.",
